{
  "text": "Structures isomorphic to the set of lines \u2113 1 , . . . , \u2113 15 occur many times in [CITATION_1] Proof. Fix a 2-coloring of [CITATION_2] n and some k \u2264 Count the number of odd lines L \u2022 \u2113 j , where L \u2208 L k and \u2113 j is one of the 15 lines of Lemma 4.1. For a fixed L, at most 14 of the lines L \u2022 \u2113 j are odd; therefore we count at most 14|L k | odd lines total.",
